Edit the configuration file and set the value of 10 seconds or
  less:

  client_body_timeout   10s;

  client_header_timeout 10s;

Edit the configuration file and set the value of
  keepalive_timeout to the value of 5 or less:

  keepalive_timeout   5 5;

Edit the configuration file and set the value of
  worker_processes to the value of auto or a value of 1 or higher:

  worker_processes auto;

